title: [Mist Harbor, Southern Walk]
description: Dark foliage, their broad leaves glistening with collected humidity, rises on either side of the wide dirt path that winds its way through jungle.  In the distance, the sound of macaws and wild animals can be heard echoing through the canopy, their harsh calls punctuated by the annoying buzz of mosquitoes and black flies.
location: the environs of the Saewehna Lagoon
